	<img data-pin-url="https://www.insidehook.com/article/health-and-fitness/how-athletes-staying-fit-home-during-coronavirus" data-pin-description="The world&#039;s fittest people are sharing their daily regimens on social media" width="1800" height="1200" src="https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?fit=1800%2C1200" class="attachment-featured-large size-featured-large wp-post-image" alt="How Pro Athletes Are Staying Fit at Home During Coronavirus" srcset="https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg 5184w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=1536,1024 1536w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=2048,1365 2048w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=1800,1200 1800w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=1200,800 1200w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=750,500 750w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=450,300 450w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=150,100 150w, https://www.insidehook.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/GettyImages-1196450833.jpg?resize=50,33 50w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" />				<div class="grid-x grid-margin-x caption-container">
			<div class="cell medium-auto caption">
									Mikaela Shiffrin of USA takes 1st place during the Audi FIS Alpine Ski World Cup. (Christophe Pallot/Agence Zoom/Getty)							</div>
