<p>Meanwhile, distance runner <a href="https://www.instagram.com/sweatandbeans/">Jesse Berube</a> shared a much-needed reminder that not having dumbbells is no excuse to skip weight training. ‚ÄúThere‚Äôs always a bodyweight exercise that‚Äôll do for now &#8230; Pick up a bag of flour, your dog or your cat, and do some #squats.</p> 



