<p>‚ÄúThis is a great workout because it&#8217;s simple. All you need is a chair and a weight. The weight could be dumbbells or a kettlebell if you have it. If you don&#8217;t, you could use a milk jug or a six pack like I did,‚Äù he says. ‚ÄúThe exercise itself works many major muscle groups like your quads, hamstrings, glutes, and shoulders. It also tests your balance.‚Äù</p> 



<p>No word yet on what he did with the beers after completing his makeshift challenge, but we‚Äôve got some ideas.</p> 



